snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance Kickstarter Teaser (2014)
snippet.description:
Missed the Kickstarter campaign? You can support the project at http://pledge.kingdomcomerpg.com/
Thanks for the support!

Original KS page: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1294225970/kingdom-come-deliverance
-------------------
Kingdom Come: Deliverance is first-person, open-world realistic RPG set in medieval Europe. Enjoy unique melee combat, castle sieges, battles and quests in this epic RPG.
http://www.kingdomcomerpg.com
http://www.warhorsestudios.cz
